âœ… 1. Folder layout (Liquibase and project are separate)

Example:

C:\Tools\liquibase-4.30.0\     â† Liquibase ZIP extracted here
C:\Projects\my-spring-app\     â† Your Spring Boot project

Inside your Spring project, create a Liquibase folder only for the changelogs, not the Liquibase program:

